<item xml:id="a2">
<locus from="1r" to="1v"/>
<desc type="Supplication"/>
<q xml:lang="gez">በረከቱ፡ ወበረከተ፡ ኵሎሙ፡ ቅዱሳን፡ መላእክት፡ የሀሉ፡ ምስለ፡ ፍቁሩ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ዳዊት። ወምስለ፡ ነፍሰ፡ አቡሁ፡ ንጉሥነ፡ ኢያሱ። ወምስለ፡ እሙ፡
ቅድስተ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ለዓለመ፡ ዓለም፡ አሜን።</q>
<note>The note states that the manuscript was written for emperor <persName role="donor" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS3430DawitII">Dāwit</persName>.
Mentioned are also his parents: emperor <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS5616IyasuI">ʾIyāsu</persName> and <persName ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS13407QeddestaKrestos">Qǝddǝsta Krǝstos</persName>.</note>
</item>

</list>

</additions>
